**Finding 2 (Suggestion) - `(window as any)` cast**: A `declare global { interface Window { __STORYBOOK_COMPODOC_JSON__?: unknown } }` block restores type safety. Low priority; pure hygiene.

**Finding 3 (Suggestion, low) - Relative `-d` path in `compodocArgs`**: Stable as-is. `{workspaceRoot}/packages/ngx-smart-components` token would be marginally more self-documenting but is not required.

